# Context API Explorer App

A comprehensive React Native application demonstrating modern mobile app architecture using React Context API for state management. Features complete authentication, theming, API integration, and smooth user experience.

## Features

### Core Requirements
- **AuthContext** - Secure login using reqres.in mock API
- **ApiContext** - Product list fetching with pagination
- **ThemeContext** - Light/Dark theme support with dynamic switching
- **Global Loader** - Full-screen animated loading indicator
- **ProductList Screen** - Display products with filtering
- **ProductDetails Screen** - Detailed product view
- **FlatList Rendering** - Optimized list performance
- **Error Handling** - Comprehensive error management
- **Navigation** - Stack navigation with auth flow

### Bonus Features (All Implemented)
- **AsyncStorage Token** - Persistent login sessions
- **Auto Login** - Automatic authentication on app launch
- **Pull-to-Refresh** - Refresh product list with swipe gesture
- **Search Bar** - Client-side product filtering
- **Pagination** - Infinite scroll for products
- **Toast Messages** - Beautiful notifications for errors/success
- **Animated Loader** - Smooth loading animations


## Architecture

src/
├── context/
│ ├── AuthContext.js # Authentication & token management
│ ├── ApiContext.js # API calls & product data
│ ├── ThemeContext.js # Light/Dark theme management
│ └── LoaderContext.js # Global loading state
├── screens/
│ ├── LoginScreen.js # User authentication
│ ├── ProductListScreen.js # Products with search & pagination
│ └── ProductDetailScreen.js # Individual product details
├── components/
│ ├── Loader.js # Animated loading component
│ └── ProductItem.js # Reusable product card
├── navigation/
│ └── AppNavigator.js # Stack navigation setup
├── config/
│ └── ToastConfig.js # Toast message configuration
└── App.js # Main app with providers

